Library for building a search engine for information retrieval. 
Able to evaluate structured queries on unstructured text as well
as implementing classical information retrieval.

There exists a docker image for strus: patrickfrey/strus-ub1404-bind
and a tutorial at http://www.project-strus.net/tutorial_MusicBrainzDataset.htm.

Interface documentation at http://patrickfrey.github.io/strus/doc/doxygen/html/index.html.

Strus project homepage at http://project-strus.net.
